#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.gammaincinv.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.special.gammaincinv"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammaincinv:1 of
msgid "Inverse to the regularized lower incomplete gamma function."
msgstr "正则化下不完全伽马函数的反函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammaincinv:3 of
msgid ""
"Given an input :math:`y` between 0 and 1, returns :math:`x` such that "
":math:`y = P(a, x)`. Here :math:`P` is the regularized lower incomplete "
"gamma function; see `gammainc`. This is well-defined because the lower "
"incomplete gamma function is monotonic as can be seen from its definition"
" in [dlmf]_."
msgstr ""
"给定一个介于 0 和 1 之间的输入 :math:`y`，返回 :math:`x` 使得 :math:`y = "
"P(a, x)`。其中 :math:`P` 是正则化下不完全伽马函数；参见 `gammainc`。这是"
"良好定义的，因为下不完全伽马函数在其定义中是单调的，可参见 [dlmf]_。"

